---
title: Garlic-Herb Beef Rump & Freekeh Salad with Roast Veggies, Yoghurt & Caramelised Onions
description: Beef and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist everyone at the table will be wanting a second helping. With flavours of garlic coming from the tender beef rump, a cooling yoghurt dolloped on top of an array of veggies and freekeh, it
can be confirmed that beef and veggies are back in the good books!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
